<br>
   can tell you to make sure you learn proper agro controll... you should be behind the tanks but ahead of the casters.  <br>
  Learn sneaking skills... you should be able to do Corpse Retrieval almost anywhere.  Little tip, sneak almost always works but only from behind, and your hide works slightly better than a combo of invisibility and invis to undead.  By dropping the first, you can check if a mob ahead of you sees the latter, then can reapply and keep going.<br>
