<br>
That being said, start making friends early.  The more you have and help along the way the more people that will remember you when you want to join parties.  You will have the most freedom of exploration of any class in the game (hide/sneak), so, use it.  Explore the land around you! <br>
<br>
As soon as you hit 10th! Party! You need to max your backstab and I think of all the ranks I have ever gotten from fighting only 3 have come from starting with a backstab solo.  This skill will be your lifesblood in a party, so max it. <br>
<br>
The rest is just have fun. Play what you like to, and see you in game. <br>
<br>
 Relanex Thines<br>
