Other then that there's nothing really special about rogue skills.  Keep abilities maxed, make an evade hotkey:<br>
<br>
/attack off<br>
/doability *<br>
/attack on<br>
<br>
Where * is the position in your ability list where you've selected the hide command (ie. if hide is in the very first ability slot you'd put a 1 there).<br>
